NexOS Server 1.0
=================
Linux 7.1 + Limine Bootloader | Server-Focused Distribution

BUILT-IN FEATURES:
------------------
- Kernel Linux 7.1 server-optimized (BBR TCP, KVM, containers, NVMe, Btrfs/XFS)
- systemd init system (networkd, timesyncd, journald)
- Nginx web server (HTTP/2, SSL, reverse proxy, load balancing)
- containerd container runtime
- Kubernetes (kubelet, kubeadm, kubectl) v1.31.0
- nftables/iptables firewall
- Docker-compatible via containerd

INSTALLATION:
-------------
Write ISO to USB/disk:
  dd if=nexos-server.iso of=/dev/sdX bs=4M status=progress

Boot from ISO, then install to disk:
  nexos-install /dev/sda

DEFAULT CREDENTIALS:
--------------------
  Username: root
  Password: nexos

SERVICES:
---------
  systemctl enable --now nginx
  systemctl enable --now containerd
  systemctl enable --now kubelet

FILESYSTEM LAYOUT:
------------------
  /var/www/html   - Web root
  /var/log        - Log files
  /var/lib/containerd - Container data
  /var/lib/kubelet    - Kubelet data
  /etc/nginx      - Nginx configuration
  /etc/containerd - Container runtime config
  /etc/kubernetes - Kubernetes config

BUILD REQUIREMENTS:
-------------------
  - GCC, make, bison, flex, bc
  - XORRISO, mtools
  - Meson, ninja (for systemd)
  - libelf-dev, libssl-dev, libcap-dev

BUILD FROM SOURCE:
------------------
  ./build.sh              - Full build (all stages)
  make kernel             - Build kernel only
  make iso                - Build final ISO
